Process called "insert_transpose_op" that takes graph as Integer, node as Integer, layout as Integer returns Nothing:
    Note: Create transpose operation node
    Note: OpKind MatrixTranspose (from node.runa)
    Let transpose_op be 11

    Let output_type be Node.get_node_output_type(node)
    Let transpose_node be Node.create_operation_node(transpose_op, output_type)

    Note: Insert transpose node in graph
    Graph.add_node(graph, transpose_node)

    Note: Redirect edges through transpose
    Note: (Simplified - real implementation would update all edges)
End Process

